definition: suffix, used to form interrogative 什麼|什么[shen2 me5], what?, indefinite 這麼|这么[zhe4 me5] thus, etc
to do/to manage/to handle/to go about/to run/to set up/to deal with

sentences.english: What if last night God destroyed my soul and put in a new soul?
sentences.chinese: 如果昨晚上帝毀掉了我的靈魂並創造了新的那怎麼辦？

sentences.english: Obviously, two, now what do I do?
sentences.chinese: 很顯然，是2，那我該怎麼辦？

sentences.english: What happens if a candidate loses their Test Report Form?
sentences.chinese: 如果考生的成績單丟失怎麼辦？

sentences.english: What if I have several million transactions?
sentences.chinese: 如果有幾百萬個事務怎麼辦？

sentences.english: Often shedding nosebleed is what reason, how should do?
sentences.chinese: 經常流鼻血是什麼原因，要怎麼辦？

sentences.english: What if you were not promoted to manager in 3 years?
sentences.chinese: 如果三年後你沒升到經理一職怎麼辦？

sentences.english: What if forget or lose the code?
sentences.chinese: 如果忘記或丟失密碼怎麼辦？

sentences.english: But the home of Kuang Heng be very poor, can not afford to buy light-on oil, how do?
sentences.chinese: 可是匡衡家裏很窮，買不起點燈的油，怎麼辦呢？

sentences.english: So I asked the other prisoners what to do.
sentences.chinese: 於是我就問其他犯人怎麼辦。

sentences.english: What do you do when people ask you for money?
sentences.chinese: 有人向你要錢的時候你會怎麼辦？

sentences.english: Q13. What if someone copies my Registered Design?
sentences.chinese: 如果有人複製我已註冊的外觀設計該怎麼辦？

sentences.english: What can they do since the children's parents were died.
sentences.chinese: 既然孩子們的父母雙亡，他們怎麼辦？

sentences.english: What if I have no debts?
What if she oversleeps and misses the bus?
sentences.chinese: 假如她睡過頭錯過班車怎麼辦？

sentences.english: What if a hurricane comes along and obliterates the dunes entirely?
sentences.chinese: 如果刮來一場颶風把沙丘都清理乾淨了怎麼辦？

sentences.english: What happens is you go overtime?

definition: (posing a question: whether sb, something) can or cannot?/is able to or not
don't tell me .../could it be that...?
what are you doing?/whatever for?/why on earth?
It is said that ... (at the start of a narrative)/to discuss/to recount
mythical horse/Internet slang for 什麼|什么[shen2 me5]
still/still in progress/still more/yet/even more/in addition/fairly/passably (good)/as early as/even/also/else
how?/how about?/how was it?/how are things?
